{"tid":1447696,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日大約四點左右，有無巴絲經過過長沙灣廣場？","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:08:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T03:21:04.000Z","uid":6707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2a1b5706ea36092a98429a96fb822f6af32b953b","tid":1447696,"uid":6707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:08:08.000Z","msg":"我諗係附近做野既巴絲都知呢間垃圾商場係紅底。每逢臨近國慶，佢地都會掛上國旗同幾個軍人擺設。<br />\n<br />\n話說今日大約四點左右經過，聽到入面有保安同疑似保安（著藍色衫同一個著便服既女人，未知身分）大聲呼喝離開/準備離開既人唔好影相。其間仲聽到個個著便服未知身分既女人，同影相既人好惡咁講：唔好影相，要影相出去影，你影相班黑衫就衝入黎架啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢咁講，係咪認為所有著住黑衫都係搞事者？同埋係咪可以咁大聲呼喝商場入面既人（我見到有客同係入面鋪頭做野既人）佢地個樣就好似黑警驅散示威者既閪樣一樣。<br />\n<br />\n我係一名和理非，我唔能夠同大家一齊係前線。我係垃圾。但我今日見到呢件事發生我就諗：我地唔應該放過任何一間紅底商場。<br />\n<br />\n但我腦袋小，除咗投訴，我諗唔到有咩可以做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位，有無咩提議可以做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傳聞呢個垃圾商場好多老鼠"},{"pid":"caefeb2427a0a84f3032ca9345f9aecde45733bd","tid":1447696,"uid":6707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:38:51.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b80b5540eab1eab723d2115c9a327806a6c35c1","tid":1447696,"uid":6707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:47:04.000Z","msg":"一齊抵制紅底，話比佢地知奶共後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"442f9873e190e7242cef232620b9c973424b603f","tid":1447696,"uid":6707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:21:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}